name: GM Star Pass Noon
short_description:
GM Star Pass Noon, a map for Garry's Mod (Steam Source SDK mapping in Hammer)
Custom models and materials are included with the download.

Download via SVN URL: http://subversion.assembla.com/svn/elvenstarnet/Gmod/checkout/maps/gm_railroads_series_1/starpass1_noon/starpass_noon.zip

Requirements:

Garry's Mod
Halflife 2
Halflife 2 Episode 2
Counter Strike Source

Optional Garry's Mod Addons:

Total Train Pack: The original train addon

Total Train Pack 2 (Not ready Yet): Gives you a variety of train props and SENTS to use.
URL to projects page:
http://code.google.com/p/the-total-train-pack-2/

Wiremod: Official Wire Addon

ENDV LS/RD Master Pack: For use with scripted trains to haul resources. Rewritten based off LS/RD2.

PHX 3: Phoenix Storms Props
summary: GM Star Pass Noon, a map for Garry's Mod
